Starting our ambassador call with Ayman Al-Hendy, MD, PhD tonight at 7pm. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We are collaborating on finding the most effective treatment. TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: My interest came from finding why fibroids are 5 times more common in women of color. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We have found certain dietary factors and environmental pollution have an effect. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We know fibroids love hormones and need hormones to grow. #TFP #Fibroids
RT @FibroidsProject: Dr.  Al-Hendy: We have found certain dietary factors and environmental pollution have an effect. #TFP #Fibroids
RT @FibroidsProject: Dr.  Al-Hendy: My interest came from finding why fibroids are 5 times more common in women of color. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: Surgery is effective, but affects the fertility potential if the patient. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: Cutting the blood supply to the fibroid shouldn't be offered to women who want to have future children. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: There is a group of medications that lowers enzymes and shrinks fibroids. TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We were able to shrink fibroids with green tea extract. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: In our study, we gave green tea extract orally for 6 months. #TFP #Fibroids
RT @FibroidsProject: Dr.  Al-Hendy: In our study, we gave green tea extract orally for 6 months. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We questioned test subjects in our study on quality of life, every month for 6 months. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: Patients who received green tea extract saw fibroids shrink by 33%. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: Connection between low vitamin D and fibroids. Women of color cannot get vitamin D from the sun. TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We can correct vitamin D deficiency easily. TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: We are now evaluating vitamin D analogs. #TFP #Fibroids
Dr.  Al-Hendy: To prevent a disease, you find the group that has the highest rate, and you have to find a way to intervene. TFP #Fibroids
